---
import AppPageLayout from "../../layouts/AppPageLayout.astro";
import { Header } from "../../app/components/Header";
import { Footer } from "../../app/components/Footer";
---

<AppPageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Pokedoku Details"
  description="Privacy policy for Pokedoku Details."
  path="/privacy-policy/"
>
  <div class="app overflow-x-hidden">
    <Header
      title="Pokedoku Details"
      subtitle="Legal information"
      currentPage="home"
      client:load
    />

    <main class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-8">
        <h1 class="m-0 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: May 7, 2026</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">Pokedoku Details does not require account registration. We may collect limited technical data such as page views and browser information through analytics tools to understand site usage.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">How We Use Information</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">We use collected information to maintain, improve, and monitor the performance of the website, and to understand which features are most useful to visitors.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">The website may use privacy-friendly analytics and similar technologies. These tools help us measure traffic and improve the user experience.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">The site links to third-party services (for example, Pokedoku, Reddit, and GitHub). Their privacy practices are governed by their own policies.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">We do not sell your personal information. We only share data when required to operate the site (such as analytics providers) or when legally required.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Policy Updates</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">We may update this policy over time. Any updates will be posted on this page and reflected in the "Last updated" date.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">If you have privacy questions, please open an issue at <a class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/jlast/pokedoku-solver/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/jlast/pokedoku-solver/issues</a>.</p>
      </article>
    </main>

    <Footer client:load />
  </div>
</AppPageLayout>
